{"tid":2489410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛國學校升國旗唱國歌　學生寫心聲：永遠效忠於中國和黨安排","createTime":"2021-04-15T02:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T02:48:48.000Z","uid":321059,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5d76aff6aa688c35f755284af3b6c0164461d5de","tid":2489410,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:42:02.000Z","msg":"愛國學校升國旗唱國歌　學生寫心聲：永遠效忠於中國和黨安排<br />\n<br />\n政府今日（15 日）舉行國家安全教育日，教育局「強烈建議」學校舉行升國旗、唱國歌等活動。親中組織香港教育工作者聯會（教聯會）營辦的黃楚標中學，進行一連 5 日的「國家安全周」，早會時間舉行升旗禮、唱國歌，播放不同學生表態支持國安法的影片。<br />\n<br />\n禮堂設有壁報板，供學生貼上「支持國安法」心聲，其中一名學生寫道，作為一名愛國人士，認為國安法是約束自己、保障公民利益和安全的良好法律措施。學生說，「<span class=\"red\">願遵守國家的一切安排，永遠效忠於中華人民共和國和黨的安排」。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n記者另觀察壁報板上的便利貼，不少學生支持國安法，<span class=\"red\">有學生指國安法「是一劑猛藥」，對香港現在的「病」加以治癒；也有學生形容香港本是繁榮穩定社會，「但是由『暴徒』們阻滯和破壞」，認為國安法適當地制裁這些「暴徒」。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/4076522095766713/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F4076522095766713%2F&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sEYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=f4e066ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/4076522095766713/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNcdZph7M6TABouh4Av1nQjBSAffsg3fWjuFa68pzh7Ft?filename=ed587BK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fed587BK.jpg&h=83156262&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c77a0be5d1f8eb38f9b8b2bac4c9de3d75a534f","tid":2489410,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:43:20.000Z","msg":"好曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515c98f4a3f7a6e868d836f1ffbeede0023cc17c","tid":2489410,"uid":14494,"like